														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4212293">
									

<p>The trick seems to be having one of the characters actively work their way towards the information so that we are only discovering it as they do. That way it's not really exposition in the sense of just being told stuff. It's an extremely clever, approach, I'm stealing it and I hope the antimimetics don't get me before I have a chance to utilise it somewhere&#8230;</p>

